{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "autosre-chaos",
  "title": "AutoSRE · Chaos Engineering",
  "tags": ["autosre", "chaos", "sre"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "editable": true,
  "time": { "from": "now-30m", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "job",
        "label": "Service",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
        "definition": "label_values(chaos_active, job)",
        "query": "label_values(chaos_active, job)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "includeAll": false,
        "multi": false,
        "current": { "text": "api", "value": "api" }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    { "id": 1, "type": "row", "title": "Current Chaos State", "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 } },
    {
      "id": 2, "type": "stat", "title": "Active Chaos Modes",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "decimals": 0, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "orange", "value": 1 } ] } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none" },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum(chaos_active{job=\"$job\"})" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3, "type": "state-timeline", "title": "Chaos Mode by Type",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 18, "x": 6, "y": 1 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "fillOpacity": 80 }, "mappings": [ { "type": "value", "options": { "0": { "text": "Off", "color": "green", "index": 0 }, "1": { "text": "Active", "color": "red", "index": 1 } } } ] }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "showValue": "auto", "mergeValues": true, "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "chaos_active{job=\"$job\"}", "legendFormat": "{{type}}" } ]
    },
    { "id": 4, "type": "row", "title": "Injection Signals", "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 9 } },
    {
      "id": 5, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Injected Latency (avg & p95)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "min": 0, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10 } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "expr": "rate(chaos_latency_seconds_sum{job=\"$job\"}[5m]) / clamp_min(rate(chaos_latency_seconds_count{job=\"$job\"}[5m]), 1e-9)", "legendFormat": "avg injected" },
        { "refId": "B", "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(chaos_latency_seconds_bucket{job=\"$job\"}[5m])))", "legendFormat": "p95 injected" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Injected Failures (HTTP 500)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 10 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "min": 0, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 20 } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "single" } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "rate(chaos_error_injections_total{job=\"$job\"}[5m])", "legendFormat": "injected 500s/s" } ]
    },
    { "id": 7, "type": "row", "title": "Resource Chaos", "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 18 } },
    {
      "id": 8, "type": "timeseries", "title": "CPU Chaos Active",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 19 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0, "max": 1, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 30, "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter" } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "single" } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "chaos_active{job=\"$job\", type=\"cpu\"}", "legendFormat": "cpu chaos" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Memory Chaos Active",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 19 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0, "max": 1, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 30, "lineInterpolation": "stepAfter" } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "single" } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "chaos_active{job=\"$job\", type=\"memory\"}", "legendFormat": "memory chaos" } ]
    },
    { "id": 10, "type": "row", "title": "Event Timeline", "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 27 } },
    {
      "id": 11, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Chaos Events (rate by type)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 28 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0, "custom": { "drawStyle": "bars", "fillOpacity": 60, "stacking": { "mode": "normal" } } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["sum"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [ { "refId": "A", "expr": "sum by (type) (rate(chaos_events_total{job=\"$job\"}[5m]))", "legendFormat": "{{type}}" } ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12, "type": "text", "title": "Full Event Log",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 28 },
      "options": { "mode": "markdown", "content": "### Chaos Event Feed\n\nThe panel to the left is a **metric-derived** timeline (counter rates by type).\n\nThe **full, row-level chaos event log** (with parameters and timestamps) is persisted as JSONL and served by the API:\n\n```\nGET /failures?source=chaos\n```\n\nA future phase wires this feed into Grafana via **Loki** (or the JSON/Infinity datasource) for a true annotated event timeline." }
    }
  ]
}
